OL,3,CWhy Starmer will struggle to recover
OL,4,Cfrom the Mandelson debacle
OL,6,FThe prime minister will look back on
OL,7,Fhis disastrous appointment of Peter
OL,8,FMandelson as US ambassador - a
OL,9,Fmisjudgement that may yet cost him his
OL,10,Fjob - as a succession of missed
OL,11,Fopportunities to avoid scoring that
OL,12,Fmost spectacular of own-goals.
OL,14,FOne such error was not to involve the
OL,15,Fthen head of the Foreign Office, Sir
OL,16,FPhilip Barton, in any part of the
OL,17,Fdecision-making process to appoint
OL,18,FMandelson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
