OL,3,CWhy Starmer will struggle to recover
OL,4,Cfrom the Mandelson debacle
OL,6,FStarmer's exclusion of Barton was
OL,7,Feccentric, to put it kindly, given
OL,8,Fthat Barton was in charge of the UK's
OL,9,Fentire diplomatic network and he had
OL,10,Fworked in Washington at a senior level.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
