OL,3,CWhy Starmer will struggle to recover
OL,4,Cfrom the Mandelson debacle
OL,6,FBarton told MPs on the Foreign Affairs
OL,7,FSelect Committee today that he was
OL,8,Finformed on December 15 that the PM
OL,9,Fhad chosen Mandelson to fill the most
OL,10,Fimportant and sensitive of all
OL,11,Fambassadorships, and that was the
OL,12,Ffirst he knew of it.
OL,14,FThe deal was done. There was nothing
OL,15,Ffor it, said Barton, than for him and
OL,16,Fthe Foreign Office to execute the PM's
OL,17,Fwill.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
