OL,3,CWhy Starmer will struggle to recover
OL,4,Cfrom the Mandelson debacle
OL,6,FHad he been asked at an earlier stage,
OL,7,Fhe would have warned the PM that
OL,8,FMandelson's Epstein links made him
OL,9,Funsuitable, because his US expertise
OL,10,Fand contacts told him Epstein was a
OL,11,Fbomb waiting to go off in Washington.
OL,13,FAs it happens, said Barton, he
OL,14,Fsubsequently revealed his Epstein
OL,15,Freservations to the PM's national
OL,16,Fsecurity adviser, Jonathan Powell.
OL,18,FBut by then it was too late. The die
OL,19,Fwas cast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
