OL,3,CWhy Starmer will struggle to recover
OL,4,Cfrom the Mandelson debacle
OL,6,FThe PM's former chief of staff, Morgan
OL,7,FMcSweeney, revealed another crossroads
OL,8,Fthat the PM manoeuvred wrongly.
OL,10,FThese were the emailed answers to
OL,11,FMcSweeney's three questions to
OL,12,FMandelson about his Epstein links.
OL,14,FMcSweeney said he still may not reveal
OL,15,Fthe details of what Mandelson wrote to
OL,16,Fhim, because the Met Police says doing
OL,17,Fso could prejudice its investigation
OL,18,Finto the former ambassador.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
