OL,3,CWhy Starmer will struggle to recover
OL,4,Cfrom the Mandelson debacle
OL,6,FBut he did reveal that he and the PM
OL,7,Fthought it was ok to appoint Mandelson
OL,8,Fbecause he said the late billionaire
OL,9,Fpaedophile Epstein was an
OL,10,Facquaintance, not a friend.
OL,12,FThis seems a quite astonishingly
OL,13,Fflimsy basis on which to make the
OL,14,Fappointment, especially since
OL,15,FMandelson admitted his
OL,16,F"acquaintanceship" with Epstein
OL,17,Fcontinued after Epstein had been
OL,18,Fimprisoned for soliciting a child for
OL,19,Fprostitution.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
