OL,3,CWhy Starmer will struggle to recover
OL,4,Cfrom the Mandelson debacle
OL,6,FI am not sure either McSweeney or
OL,7,FStarmer can stay afloat on a raft
OL,8,Fbuilt on the idea that Epstein was
OL,9,F"only" an acquaintance of Mandelson.
OL,11,FThat said, today's proceedings in
OL,12,Fparliament are all about whether the
OL,13,FPM lied to MPs that due process had
OL,14,Fbeen followed in Mandelson's
OL,15,Fappointment and in saying pressure had
OL,16,Fnot been imposed on the Foreign Office
OL,17,Fto expedite vetting.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
