OL,3,CWhy Starmer will struggle to recover
OL,4,Cfrom the Mandelson debacle
OL,6,FBarton's evidence today on these
OL,7,Fquestions harmed the PM's cause - he
OL,8,Fcouldn't bring himself to say whether
OL,9,Fdue process had been followed, though
OL,10,Fhe did say vetting should have
OL,11,Fhappened before Mandelson was given
OL,12,Fthe job - but the overall picture is
OL,13,Fperhaps nuanced.
OL,15,FWhat is not nuanced is that a normally
OL,16,Fmethodical and risk-averse prime
OL,17,Fminister made the most
OL,18,Fcatastrophically reckless decisions in
OL,19,Fchoosing Mandelson in the first place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
